    "Here, the data are presented in the numpy array format, and every motion has a dimension calledjoints_num and motion_length.",
    "Sample signals used for the validation are shown in Fig. 2.Here, the EEG /EMG signals utilized for the validations are specified as Sig In j, were j = 1, 2,..., J and the EEG/EMG signals for the validation are presented as J.Sensor Measure Data: In this phase, sensor data used for the validation are obtained from the MotionID: IMU-specific motion dataset 40.",
    "Here, the dataset is used to execute the user verification through human motion, and the data are presented in Bin format.",
    "Moreover, the dataset holds samples of 50 h of inertial measurement units with single motion patterns collected from 101 users.",
    "In the dataset, smartphones are used to collect the data from 101 users, who used the Smartphone 300 times from the table in different locations.Sensor measure data used for the analysis are signified as Da IN r, where r = 1, 2,..., R, and all the sensor measures are indicated as R. Development of an adaptive hybrid network for human motion intention predictionThe developed work employs the two primary networks such as AH-CNN-LSTM and AH-CNN-Res-LSTM for predicting the human motion intention."
